Package edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.manager

Class AppList

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.manager.AppList
public class AppList extends Object
AppList maintains and manages a list of Applications. Provides methods to add, delete, retrieve, and manipulate applications.
Author:
Anoushka Piduru
